</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_50" id="24r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Reinharten von Wallsee, hauptman ob der
                        Ens</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Anna, des Hansen Eyrings
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers eliche <expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan>, von
            iren und <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> irs wirts wegen, wie daz sie etwaz sache mit
            Hansen Smyd, der <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<add><expan>Anne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>prud<ex>er</ex></expan></add>, <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> czu Enns, mit dem
            rehten czu handeln <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das in etwielang verczogen sey worden,
            als sie das <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell selber auch wol
              <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> werden. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> Hansen <expan>Eyring<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan> durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>fürderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein wöllet, daz in <add>von
                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>H<ex>ans</ex></expan> Smyd</add>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czoge<ex>n</ex></expan> sleunig reht widerfare. Als etc. Das
                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Barthol<ex>omei</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
